---
import "../styles/global.css";
---
<section class="flex flex-wrap gap-5 justify-center items-center px-11 py-28 mt-20 w-full rounded-3xl bg-sky-950 min-h-[682px] shadow-[0px_4px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] max-md:px-5 max-md:py-24 max-md:mt-10 max-md:max-w-full">
  <article class="self-stretch my-auto text-xl font-bold text-white min-h-[460px] min-w-60 w-[282px]">
    <h2 class="text-4xl">Comunicate con Nosotros</h2>
    <p class="mt-5">
      Recupera tu tiempo libre y disfruta de un espacio impecable. En Soma,
      nos encargamos de dejar tu hogar o negocio reluciente para que t√∫ te
      enfoques en lo que realmente importa.
    </p>
    <address class="mt-5 leading-7 not-italic">
      Telefono: 099878767<br />
      Instagram: @Mipatriaec<br />
      Alborada Decima Etapainfosoma@soma.com
    </address>
  </article>

  <img
    src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/e2bad942d84a84fe3157fd5520fbc818d4dda7f8?placeholderIfAbsent=true&apiKey=2ae942d826f94e6aab2cf449d09e4472"
    alt="Contact illustration"
    class="object-contain shrink-0 self-stretch my-auto rounded-3xl aspect-[0.64] min-w-60 w-[283px]"
  />

  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-end self-stretch my-auto h-[456px] min-w-60 w-[414px]">
    <div class="pt-5 max-w-full text-white w-[413px]">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Separa hoy tu cita</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xl font-medium">Deja eso que te quita tu tiempo</p>
    </div>

    <form class="mt-11 w-full text-base whitespace-nowrap max-w-[413px] text-zinc-500 max-md:mt-10">
      <div class="flex gap-3.5 w-full">
        <input
          type="text"
          placeholder="Nombre"
          class="gap-2.5 self-stretch px-5 py-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[52px]"
          required
        />
        <input
          type="tel"
          placeholder="Numero"
          class="gap-2.5 self-stretch px-5 py-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[52px]"
          required
        />
      </div>

      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="Correo"
        class="gap-2.5 self-stretch px-5 py-4 mt-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[52px] w-full"
        required
      />

      <textarea
        placeholder="Mensaje"
        class="gap-2.5 px-5 pt-2.5 pb-24 mt-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[127px] w-full"
        required
      ></textarea>

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="gap-2.5 self-stretch px-2.5 py-4 mt-4 text-white bg-sky-900 rounded-3xl min-h-[52px] w-full hover:bg-sky-800 transition-colors"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
